{"tid":1579731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「區選」黃絲人人都要係助選員！！！","createTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T01:37:15.000Z","uid":160551,"like":174,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"43780a397d08efcd4d2ed1ab501a61b0b5559c27","tid":1579731,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"黎緊區選 黃絲必須要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全民皆兵</span></span>先可以有更大既贏面<br />\n<br />\n當你諗下 人人都係助選員 只要每個黃絲得閒 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落街幫手</span></span>一兩個鐘派下傳單叫下口號，你地諗下個場面有幾大！！點都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">贏晒</span></span>建制派既C9啊婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須</span></span>要推廣 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民黃絲助選團！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPs:希望文宣見到會幫手推廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f71459bebf963bed8bd1091c0d2ed3605a37cd3f","tid":1579731,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbb461f81b73f9188d14cecf6c2b0a2796b6818","tid":1579731,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ee6de5c0c32c3846bbe4cb62bbfc521afcea01f","tid":1579731,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"[907機場] 詳細分析907狗畜當日佈防及策略，附未來破陣建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a91a3905a8f7bd9be4aa5e4e1f2a501eda6530b2","tid":1579731,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:59