43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef69cbf730e322414df9ebf381d2ebae2fb94497","tid":1579731,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"仲有每人都要拉十票投非保皇派<br />\n不講咩區 親戚朋友同事同學都好<br />\n200萬人出黎遊過行<br />\n但區議會單議席單票制都唔去投<br />\n好意思話五大訴求 缺一不可？<br />\n港共政府可能舞弊出千係一回事<br />\n唔去投票點對得住死去既義士<br />\n點對得住受傷被捕被虐被姦既手足"},{"pid":"3fc12e41d14f39874fd25cb9cd0b8a32ff5efa3d","tid":1579731,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11128ee59b4b353235d2748687ac17fb26ae6c1","tid":1579731,"uid":294115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"反而想問，技術上咩情況下選舉失效，區議會真空？"},{"pid":"9b8b596c60a2abfc60ebba7981bb772b7582463f","tid":1579731,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03494cab07db6468750156a7dceb11f84d04edf2","tid":1579731,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ac316c0361427c8c3d06a1b54d3aa380329458c","tid":1579731,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e743ffd1b3013d7f0e59485671b380674f47343e","tid":1579731,"uid":302618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"我記得填報選舉開支好似係要報埋其他人幫印嘅海報？唔肯定，留名等睇熟程序嘅巴絲解答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"即係可以用助選budget做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"即係如果我地幫手印，會打亂/打爆條數？<br />\n好似係話選舉開支有上限，選舉經理唔可以用多於規定嘅金額去宣傳？"},{"pid":"0493d5c80343b9c186b2de19d3509efd6ee2ff55","tid":1579731,"uid":196091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b8b596c60a2abfc60ebba7981bb772b7582463f","tid":1579731,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0