距離）係有規定不可以掛宣傳品阻礙行人，呢啲規定到時可以上網睇，遇到懷疑違規請影相拍片腥去 1823，reo<br />\n<br />\n如果裁定違規，正苦（以前）會警告甚至搵人移除，費用會搵違規果個候選人追收 （而家跟唔跟規矩做就唔知鳥）"},{"pid":"538c21bce003dbd691fd229f044956fdd8f0e2c1","tid":1579731,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f4c6e9d4259444028992ff89fa2e5da82e7ad15","tid":1579731,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:24:26.000Z","msg":"1/10都未到就出黎食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5eb8a37bf9b13962175aa4a7f58938b87be5a5","tid":1579731,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c6e0183f26d43af74d929d3d0e2560ffd42c44","tid":1579731,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:38:39.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！"},{"pid":"e0f621822ddd8a3d18294daa8c0ca4c01649e094","tid":1579731,"uid":33077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:41:52.000Z","msg":"有無文宣叻既人整個18區list 分類d 候選人<br />\n我個區就有譚文豪,佢好似個助理出黎選(我認我無留意清楚)<br />\n佢上星期樂富街站俾人攪 ,得兩個女仔,好oo係個阿叔搞<br />\n我落去見到已經有popo<br />\n我下次補返個名<br />\n我知都有人覺得公民黨都係鬼鬼地,但我個日黃大仙見到譚文豪,佢真係有做野<br />\n<br />\n但點都好過 民建聯 同工聯會 仲有葉瘤新民黨"},{"pid":"08b661348d617749e22e4d5ef42e3fa127eab5c3","tid":1579731,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T22:02:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a26d0816a069a1f025313bce8be209b7929ced56","tid":1579731,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T22:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719e73f382626cfdad20ca5335a8aae6044900